Description: Calendar and schedule panel applet for COSMIC desktop
 A panel applet for the COSMIC desktop environment that displays
 the current date and time, with a popup showing a calendar grid
 and your upcoming events.
 .
 Features include calendar navigation, day-by-day event viewing,
 one-click join for video calls, and flexible display options.
